headline.print_headline: US Officials: Liberty Reserve Founder Extradited
headline.main: US Officials: Liberty Reserve Founder Extradited

lead_paragraph: Authorities say a man accused of being behind one of the world's biggest money-laundering businesses has been extradited from Spain to the U.S. to face charges.
